<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>456</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Kumthar dang khua a dei cang, Maw kan dawt Pa Pathian, Nangmah he tuan
 tinak kum, Run siter ko rih law, Thang-thatnak le than-chonak kum zongah
 run ser ko, Kan sin na um zungzal nak, Tu kum zong langhter ko.

[V2]
 Dawtnak kum thar a dei cang, Nun than dawtnak um seh, Na mithmai
 chungah lawmhnak, Ni bangin a tlang cang, Na dawt tang cung kumthar
 chung, Hngat-channak um ko seh, Lungdai le lung-lawmhnak in, Dinhnak
 kumthar dei seh.

[V3]
 Nangmah ca'h rian kan tuan lai, Na dawtnak a lang lai, Vancung rian
 tha ruahchan in, Kumthar chung kantuan lai, Kumthar dang khua a dei cang,
 Maw kan dawt Pa Pathian, Van le lei khua zakip ah, Kumthar nang ca'h
 siseh.</lyrics>
<key>Eb</key>
<title>KUM THAR DANG KHUA A DEI CANG CH456</title>
</song>